title: Humble Yourself
itunes:title: Humble Yourself
description:
Episode 181 - You're selfish, but don't worry we all are. When you get wrapped up in your problems, your worries and the things that you want you are only thinking about yourself. In this episode I talk about how to humble yourself, be happier and rid yourself of a scarcity mindset.
